v1.1
- MySql database connection updated to MySql5 - Guids now are stored as BINARY(16)
- log4net library used - Now SMSSender logs onto a log.txt file in the binary folder.
  Log file rolls as soon as it reaches 200KB in size. 50 total files are stored. log4net configuration
  can be easily changed through SMSSenderService.exe.config file in the binary folder.
  
v0.1
- First Release